item.title: Gadwal: Public Auction of 73 Abandoned Vehicles on January 30
item.description:
<![CDATA[Gadwal: A public auction of 73 unidentified (scrub) vehicles, currently in police custody, will be held on January 30, 2025, at 11:00 AM. The auction will take place at the Police Armed Forces Office premises in Gadwal PJP Camp, as announced by District SP T. Srinivasa Rao
Since the deadline for the victims to identify and claim their vehicles has expired, the remaining unclaimed vehicles will be auctioned. Interested bidders can view the vehicles to be auctioned on the day before the event, Ja...]]>
